More Info About ConforMIS, Inc. (CFMS)

ConforMIS is a medical technology company that uses its proprietary iFit Image-to-Implant technology platform to develop, manufacture and sell joint replacement implants that are individually sized and shaped, or customized, to fit each patient’s unique anatomy. The company was founded in 2004 and is based in Bedford, Massachusetts. View our full CFMS ticker page with ratings, news, and more.
 






 


