Company Profile
Sector: Health Care
Industry: Medical Equipment & Devices
Sub-Industry: Medical Equipment
ConforMIS Inc. develops and manufactures knee implants. The Company offers femoral and tibial knee implants for the treatment of osteoarthritis and joint damages. ConforMIS markets its products and services to orthopedic surgeons and orthopedic surgical centers throughout the United States.




