Product
Conformis iTotal CR-Cruciate Retaining Knee Replacement System Model Numbers:M57250600010   iTotal CR, Left KneeM57250600020 iTotal CR, Right KneeProduct Usage :  Usage:The iTotal CR Knee Replacement System (KRS) is intended for use as a total knee replacement in patients with knee joint pain and disability whose conditions cannot be solely addressed by the use of a prosthetic device that treats only one or two of the three knee compartments, such as a unicondylar, patello-femoral or bi-compartmental prosthesis.


